OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FThe owners of a village pub in Kent
OL,8,Ffear a long term road closure will
OL,9,Fforce them out of business and leave
OL,10,Fthem homeless.
OL,12,FThe couple run the Four Horseshoes in
OL,13,FGraveney and says 5 months of rolling
OL,14,Froadworks for water pipe replacement
OL,15,Fwould cut off most of their customers
OL,16,Facross some of the busiest months of
OL,17,Fthe year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
