PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FSouth East Water says the work will
OL,8,Freduce the chance of leaks, but
OL,9,Fbusinesses in the area are calling for
OL,10,Fthe works to be re-arranged.
OL,12,FThe Four Horseshoes, near Faversham,
OL,13,Fhas been serving the Graveney area for
OL,14,Falmost 300 years.
OL,16,FThe current owners fear a second road
OL,17,Fclosure in 12 months could force them
OL,18,Fout of business and out of their home
OL,19,F- as South East Water plans months of
OL,20,Frolling road closures.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FPublican Chris Goater said: "It could
OL,8,Fshut us down, you know, it could make
OL,9,Fus homeless."
OL,11,F"We've been through the difficult
OL,12,Fperiod when the road was closed last
OL,13,Fyear. Luckily we survived that, we
OL,14,Fknow we had great support from the
OL,15,Flocals. And, you know, if it's going
OL,16,Fto happen again we haven't got a back
OL,17,Fup plan. We spent our back up plan
OL,18,Flast year."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FKatrina Goater added: "They shut this
OL,8,Froad and we lose our business. We also
OL,9,Flose our house, my children are made
OL,10,Fhomeless.
OL,12,F"You know, the pub's been here 300
OL,13,Fyears and it's such a shame they're
OL,14,Fnot taking into account the small
OL,15,Fbusinesses in the area."
OL,17,FThe Goaters say the road closures will
OL,18,Fcover summer months, fireworks night,
OL,19,FHalloween and the festive period,
OL,20,Fwhich are important times for the
OL,21,Fhospitality trade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FThe couple said they appreciate that
OL,8,FSouth East Water is doing the work to
OL,9,Freplace worn out infrastructure, and
OL,10,Fthat the work has to be done, but
OL,11,Fthey're calling for it to be postponed
OL,12,Fto January.
OL,14,FAnother local business, Top Knot
OL,15,FAlpacas, said: "This closure will have
OL,16,Fa huge impact on my business because
OL,17,Fwe get a lot of footfall from people
OL,18,Fthat are holidaymakers and traffic
OL,19,Fthat's passing by.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,F"I would agree that especially the way
OL,8,Fwater is right now, it's really
OL,9,Fimportant to repair the water mains. I
OL,10,Ffully support that, I just feel that
OL,11,Fthe businesses should be considered.
OL,12,FThe time of year is wrong to do this
OL,13,Fat the end of the summer and right the
OL,14,Fway through till Christmas."
OL,16,FSouth East Water says the closure is
OL,17,Fnecessary for the safety of motorists,
OL,18,Fpedestrians and their workforce. And
OL,19,Freplacing around 700 metres of water
OL,20,Fmains will "reduce the risk of future
OL,21,Fleaks and bursts".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1783691326
OL,3,CPub fears road closures will force
OL,4,Cthem out of business and leave them
OL,5,Chomeless
OL,7,FThey added that that teams will work
OL,8,Fsome extended hours to reduce
OL,9,Fdisruption. And work will pause from
OL,10,FDecember 11 to the New Year for the
OL,11,Fbusy trading period.
OL,13,FBut for the publicans at the Four
OL,14,FHorseshoes, the concern is whether the
OL,15,Fbusiness can survive until then.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
